  - may be to do with the tab being put to sleep or something

game features
-------------

- a playable game (v1.0)
  - index.html with options for playing standard levels or daily levels
  - finish a level
  - remember progress in localstorage
  - repair all the JSON output stuff and make it more dynamic 
    - x is a spirit, X is a spirit in earth
- levels should have short descriptions
- banners before each level e.g. "get all the diamonds!" "rocks fall when not supported"

- v2 map builder
  - random WxH box filled with stuff
  - has a random exit
  - a tunnel of random length
  - then another WxH random box

